{"tid":583831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6男闖投資公司嘈交 爆樽架頸與警對峙","createTime":"2018-03-07T10:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T10:37:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6aeccdb79fd3e195108e0158a12fa9822ae7bd00","tid":583831,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180307/large/1520418074_3d03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180307%2Flarge%2F1520418074_3d03.jpg&h=2f3a1622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴發生對峙事件，下午3時許，6名男子闖入廣東道30號一間投資公司的寫字樓，與職員發生爭執，其間有人打爆玻璃樽架頸，揚言自殘，職員慌忙報案。警員接報趕至持盾牌上樓戒備，消防處亦派出兩部救護車到場。雙方對峙近3小時，警方召談判專家進行遊說。"}]}